ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-germany-afd-support-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupport%20for%20far-right%20parties%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20spreading%20of%20misinformation%20is%20just%20disgraceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f8d0f87-3eb2-4212-9028-7810af57b1f6%5C%22%3EModel%203%20woes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20honest%2C%20I%20never%20really%20liked%20the%20Model%203%20that%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20denying%20that%20when%20you%20first%20got%20in%2C%20it%20was%20exciting.%20You%20put%20your%20foot%20down%2C%20and%20it%20goes%20very%20fast.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20not%20very%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seats%20weren't%20well%20made%2C%20and%20the%20interior%20was%20cheap%20and%20nasty.%20Many%20of%20the%20important%20settings%20were%20adjusted%20via%20the%20display%20screen%2C%20so%20your%20eyes%20were%20off%20the%20road%20when%20they%20should%20have%20been%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20doors%20weren't%20fitted%20that%20well%2C%20so%20you%20got%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20cabin%20noise%2C%20and%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20suspension%20started%20squeaking%20heavily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20just%20felt%20cheap.%20Personally%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20it%20was%20very%20well%20put%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20service%20was%20OK%2C%20but%20after%20a%20few%20years%2C%20the%20response%20was%20awful.%20It's%20probably%20the%20worst%20service%20I've%20ever%20had%20from%20any%20car%20dealer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20sold%20the%20Tesla%2C%20it%20had%20the%20worst%20depreciation%20of%20any%20car%20I've%20ever%20owned.%20We%20sold%20it%20for%20just%20over%20%C2%A310%2C000%20%5B%2413%2C500%5D%20after%20buying%20it%20for%20nearly%20%C2%A350%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BTesla%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229aa4e378-2ec1-4709-90c5-31ce9e1c5a3b%5C%22%3EBuying%20a%20BYD%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20next%20to%20a%20BYD%20Seal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687f599b3d5881a51c1dbbd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20Bond%20bought%20his%20BYD%20Seal%20secondhand%20after%20previously%20owning%20a%20Tesla%20Model%203.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Bond%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20car%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20we%20would%20have%20to%20compromise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20found%20was%20that%20there%20are%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20cars%20that%20have%20caught%20up%20and%20overtaken%20Tesla%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%2C%20but%20also%20on%20range%20and%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20the%20BYD%20Seal%20around%20the%20same%20time%20we%20sold%20the%20Tesla.%20We%20bought%20an%20ex-demonstrator%20vehicle%20that%20was%20a%20year%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20quicker%20than%20the%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20it%20accelerates%20from%200%20to%20100km%2Fh%20in%203.8%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20has%20a%20longer%20range.%20You%20can%20also%20charge%20it%20to%20100%25%20without%20damaging%20the%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20a%20beautifully%20built%20car%2C%20and%20very%20comfortable.%20If%20you%20shut%20the%20doors%2C%20they%20go%20thunk%2C%20as%20they%20should%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20wind%20noise%20in%20the%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20got%20ambient%20lighting%2C%20vented%20seats%2C%20and%20head-up%20displays%2C%20all%20the%20things%20that%20you%20might%20expect%20in%20a%20car%20that%20you%20pay%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20find%20things%20to%20fault%20with%20it.%20The%20media%20system%20is%20a%20bit%20clunky%20and%20glitchy%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20tiny%20bit%20slower%20to%20charge.%20However%2C%20we%20do%20most%20of%20our%20charging%20at%20home%2C%20and%20with%20the%20Seal%20having%20more%20range%2C%20the%20slower%20charge%20time%20isn't%20really%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20drives%20beautifully%20on%20the%20road.%20You%20would%20put%20it%20through%20a%20corner%20in%20a%20way%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20drive%20in%20the%20Tesla.%20It%20feels%20safe%20and%20it%20feels%20solid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20could%20give%20scores%2C%20I'd%20give%20the%20BYD%20nine%20out%20of%20ten%20and%20probably%20one%20out%20of%20ten%20for%20the%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20swapped%20your%20Tesla%20for%20a%20BYD%20or%20bought%20a%20Chinese%20EV%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atcarter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Etcarter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswapped-tesla-model-3-for-a-byd-seal-elon-musk-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753176638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687f5904f748d8c055f603b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswapped-tesla-model-3-for-a-byd-seal-elon-musk-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kevin%20Bond%20bought%20a%20Tesla%20Model%203%20with%20his%20pension%20after%20he%20retired.%20He%20told%20BI%20he%20swapped%20it%20for%20a%20BYD%20Seal%20partly%20because%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswapped-tesla-model-3-for-a-byd-seal-elon-musk-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dubai%20launches%20One%20Freezone%20Passport%20that%20unlocks%20access%20to%20all%20free%20zones%3B%20Louis%20Vuitton%20first%20to%20join%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22