w.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-impersonating-elon-musk-unprompted-violation-xai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpersonating%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recently%2C%20some%20were%20also%20asked%20to%20record%20their%20facial%20expressions%20to%20train%20the%20LLM%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20weren't%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20more%20than%20200%20employees%20took%20part%20in%20an%20internal%20project%20called%20%26quot%3BSkippy%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20involved%20recording%20videos%20of%20themselves%20to%20help%20train%20the%20AI%20model%20to%20interpret%20human%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20documents%20and%20Slack%20messages%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20show%20that%20the%20project%20left%20many%20workers%20uneasy%2C%20with%20some%20raising%20alarms%20about%20how%20their%20likenesses%20might%20be%20used.%20Others%20opted%20out%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20weeklong%20period%2C%20AI%20tutors%20%E2%80%94%20the%20workers%20who%20help%20train%20Grok%2C%20the%20company's%20large%20language%20model%20%E2%80%94%20were%20tasked%20with%20recording%20videos%20of%20themselves%20speaking%20to%20coworkers%20as%20well%20as%20making%20facial%20expressions%2C%20internal%20documents%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20was%20designed%20to%20train%20the%20company's%20AI%20model%20to%20%26quot%3Brecognize%20and%20analyze%20facial%20movements%20and%20expressions%2C%20such%20as%20how%20people%20talk%2C%20react%20to%20others'%20conversations%2C%20and%20express%20themselves%20in%20various%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20one%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tutors%20were%20scheduled%20for%2015-%20to%2030-minute%20conversations%20with%20their%20coworkers.%20One%20person%20played%20the%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bhost%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20virtual%20assistant%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20other%20would%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20a%20user.%20The%20%26quot%3Bhost%26quot%3B%20minimized%20their%20movements%20and%20prioritized%20proper%20framing%2C%20while%20those%20playing%20the%20user%20could%20operate%20off%20a%20cellphone%20camera%20or%20computer%20and%20move%20freely%20in%20order%20to%20simulate%20a%20casual%20conversation%20with%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20whether%20that%20training%20data%20had%20any%20role%20in%20powering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-ai-companion-inspired-edward-cullen-christian-gray-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERudi%20and%20Ani%2C%20two%20lifelike%20avatars%20that%20xAI%20released%20last%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20quickly%20shown%20stripping%2C%20flirting%2C%20and%20threatening%20to%20bomb%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20engineer%20on%20the%20project%20told%20workers%20during%20an%20introductory%20meeting%20that%20the%20project%20would%20help%20%26quot%3Bgive%20Grok%20a%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20recording%20viewed%20by%20BI.%20The%20project%20lead%20said%20that%20the%20company%20might%20eventually%20use%20the%20data%20to%20build%20out%20%26quot%3Bavatars%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20lead%20said%20xAI%20wanted%20imperfect%20data%20%E2%80%94%20background%20noise%20and%20sudden%20movements%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20AI%20system%20would%20be%20more%20limited%20in%20its%20responses%20if%20it%20were%20trained%20solely%20on%20perfect%20video%20and%20audio%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20told%20staff%20that%20the%20videos%20would%20not%20be%20distributed%20outside%20the%20company%2C%20and%20were%20solely%20for%20training%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20face%20will%20not%20ever%20make%20it%20to%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20engineer%20on%20the%20project%20told%20workers%20during%20the%20kick-off%20call.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20purely%20to%20teach%20Grok%20what%20a%20face%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20were%20given%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20have%20a%20successful%20one-on-one%20conversation%2C%20including%20avoiding%20one-word%20answers%2C%20asking%20follow-up%20questions%2C%20and%20maintaining%20eye%20contact.%20The%20company%20also%20supplied%20staff%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20conversation%20topics.%20Examples%20included%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20secretly%20manipulate%20people%20to%20get%20your%20way%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20showers%3F%20Do%20you%20prefer%20morning%20or%20night%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20ever%20date%20someone%20with%20a%20kid%20or%20kids%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20filming%2C%20workers%20were%20required%20to%20sign%20a%20consent%20form%20granting%20xAI%20%26quot%3Bperpetual%26quot%3B%20access%20to%20the%20data%2C%20including%20the%20workers'%20%26quot%3Blikeness%26quot%3B%20for%20training%20and%20also%20for%20%26quot%3Binclusion%20in%20and%20promotion%20of%20commercial%20products%20and%20services%20offered%20by%20xAI.%26quot%3B%20The%20form%20specified%20the%20data%20would%20be%20used%20for%20training%20purposes%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20create%20a%20digital%20version%20of%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20workers%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20use%20of%20the%20data%20and%20the%20consent%20form%2C%20and%20several%20said%20they%20chose%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20the%20program%2C%20according%20to%20Slack%20messages%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20general%20concern%20is%20if%20you're%20able%20to%20use%20my%20likeness%20and%20give%20it%20that%20sublikeness%2C%20could%20my%20face%20be%20used%20to%20say%20something%20I%20never%20said%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20worker%20said%20during%20the%20introductory%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20xAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20xAI%20launched%20a%20feature%20that%20allowed%20users%20to%20video%20chat%20with%20Grok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2014%2C%20the%20company%20released%20its%20Ani%20and%20Rudi%20avatars%2C%20a%20few%20days%