0person%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%2C%20citing%20their%20ongoing%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20seemed%20like%20a%20very%20reasonable%2C%20empathetic%2C%20competent%20scientist%20who%20embraced%20travel%20and%20being%20in%20foreign%20cultures.%26quot%3B%20The%20former%20colleague%20described%20Maguire%20as%20having%20a%20sense%20of%20mission%20and%20being%20concerned%20about%20national%20security%20issues%20without%20seeming%20ideological.%20Afghanistan%20was%20another%20stop%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-sad-decline-lonely-planet-america-coolest-travel-guide-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebackpacker's%20adventure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227135%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shaun%20Maguire%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687e815bf748d8c055f5fa36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224757%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaguire%20at%20the%202025%20Hill%20%26amp%3B%20Valley%20Forum.%3Cp%3EBRENDAN%20SMIALOWSKI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Maguire%20and%20some%20of%20his%20DARPA%20colleagues%2C%20including%20Tim%20Junio%2C%20a%20CIA%20analyst-turned-CEO%2C%20spun%20out%20a%20startup%20called%20Qadium%2C%20which%20worked%20with%20government%20and%20industry%20clients%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frip-goldman-sachs-wall-street-investment-bank-dead-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20secure%20their%20systems.%20Peter%20Thiel's%20Founders%20Fund%20was%20an%20early%20backer.%20Qadium%20later%20rebranded%20itself%20as%20Expanse%20and%20was%20sold%20to%20cybersecurity%20giant%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%20for%20about%20%241%20billion%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20VC%20who%20worked%20with%20Maguire%20and%20Qadium%20described%20him%20in%20admiring%20terms.%20%26quot%3BShaun%20is%20somebody%20who%20just%20knows