20job.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Sequoia%2C%20where%20he%20has%20the%20general%20partner%20position%20denied%20to%20him%20at%20GV%2C%20Maguire%20has%20become%20known%20for%20investing%20in%20Musk's%20companies%2C%20including%20the%20Twitter%20acquisition%2C%20The%20Boring%20Company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-pressed-workers-install-surveillance-software-personal-laptops-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ExAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20SpaceX.%20On%20X%2C%20Maguire%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-worker-7-years-resigned-elon-musk-mission-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20chummy%2C%20sharing%20each%20other's%20posts%20and%20offering%20supportive%20emojis%2C%20especially%20when%20Western%20civilization%20is%20at%20stake.%20In%20a%20recent%20video%2C%20Maguire%20said%20that%20his%20paper%20returns%20for%20Sequoia%20were%20approaching%20%2410%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20status%20at%20the%20firm%20is%20predicated%20on%20his%20relationship%20with%20Elon.%20He's%20an%20Elon%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20vice%20president%20at%20one%20of%20Sequoia's%20limited%20partners.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20made%20incredible%20returns%20on%20SpaceX%20and%20some%20of%20the%20other%20Elon-backed%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Biggar%2C%20a%20tech%20entrepreneur%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Tech%20for%20Palestine%2C%20an%20incubator%20for%20activist%20groups%20involved%20with%20the%20open%20letter%2C%20has%20sparred%20with%20Maguire.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20not%20know%20this...%20but%20I've%20been%20watching%20you%20%F0%9F%91%80%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20recently%20wrote%20on%20X.%20Biggar%20called%20the%20message%20a%20threat%20and%20demanded%20that%20Sequoia%20investigate.%20Biggar%20thinks%20that%20Maguire's%20connection%20with%20Musk%20is%20overrated.%20%26quot%3BSequoia%20doesn't%20need%20a%20racist%20partner%20to%20talk%20to%20Elon%20Musk%2C%26quot%3B%20Biggar%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeaded%20by%20Botha%2C%20PayPal's%20former%20CFO%2C%20Sequoia%20has%20no%20official%20political%20alignment%3B%20prominent%20partners%20like%20Doug%20Leone%20and%20Michael%20Moritz%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-tech-industry-war-against-media-journalists-podcasts-broletariat-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emajor%20donors%20to%20the%20Republican%20and%20Democratic%20parties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20respectively.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20proud%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we've%20enabled%20many%20of%20our%20partners%20to%20express%20their%20respective%20individual%20views%20along%20the%20way%2C%20and%20given%20them%20that%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20Botha%20said%20at%20a%20conference%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESequoia%20seems%20to%20have%20kept%20a%20hands-off%20approach%20regarding%20Maguire's%20rising%20notoriety%2C%20and%20there%20may%20be%20little%20risk%20in%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20way%20this%20progressed%2C%20and%20because%20Sequoia%20didn't%20shut%20this%20down%20super%20early%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20could%20do%20anything%20about%20it%20at%20this%20point%2C%20even%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20VC%20who%20knows%20Maguire.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20delivered%20good%20returns%20for%20Sequoia.%20Just%20because%20he%20has%20strong%20political%20views%20doesn't%20mean%20he's%20not%20meriting%20of%20a%20role%20as%20a%20partner%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaguire%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20his%20views.%20Very%20much%20in%20line%20with%20a%20rising%20ethos%20in%20the%20VC%20and%20founder%20class%2C%20he%20holds%20himself%20out%20as%20a%20warrior%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20American%20ideal%2C%20a%20patriot%20investing%20in%20the%20country%20and%20helping%20defend%20it%20from%20its%20enemies.%20The%20VC%20firm%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20calls%20it%20American%20Dynamism.%20It's%20the%20same%20proudly%20jingoistic%20attitude%20seen%20in%20industry%20eminences%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-tech-founders-skipping-college-new-dropping-out-palantir-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPalantir%20CEO%20Alex%20Karp%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Anduril%20CEO%20Palmer%20Luckey.%20It's%20why%20Founders%20Fund%20is%20getting%20into%20the%20action-movie%20business.%20%26quot%3BWestern%20Civilization%20is%20approaching%20the%20Event%20Horizon%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20recently%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20max%20thrust%20our%20boosters%20in%20the%20other%20direction%20we're%20not%20gonna%20make%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wasn't%20always%20like%20this.%20People%20who%20knew%20him%20pointed%20to%20his%20GV%20experience%20and%20Hamas'%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20as%20milestones%20on%20his%20journey%20toward%20the%20inner%20circle%20of%20tech's%20new%20right-wing%20elite.%20Maguire%20has%20also%20written%20at%20length%20about%20his%20own%20political%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20in%202016%20I%20had%20drunk%20the%20media%20Kool-Aid%20and%20was%20scared%20out%20of%20my%20mind%20about%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20wrote%20in%20a%20May%202024%20post%20endorsing%20Trump.%20%26quot%3BAs%20such%20I%20donated%20to%20Hilary%20Clinton's%20campaign%20and%20voted%20for%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaguire%20said%20that%20he%20didn't%20vote%20in%202020%20and%20that%20he%20turned%20against%20the%20Biden%20administration%20after%20its%20withdrawal%20of%20US%20forces%20from%20Afghanistan%20was%20accompanied%20by%20deadly%20bombings%20and%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20US-installed%20government.%20After%20October%207%2C%20Maguire%20thought%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20was%20responding%20with%20weakness%2C%20especially%20toward%20Iran.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20start%20looking%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20see%20anything%20other%20than%20Iranian%20foreign%20influence%20in%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20now%20Maguire's%20posts%20often%20came%20laden%20with%20MAGA%20shibboleths%20about%20the%20corrupt%20legacy%20media%2C%20anti-Trump%20lawfare%2C%20and%20woke%20politics.%20He%20touted%20a%20%24300%2C000%20donation%20he%20made%20to%20a%20pro-Donald%20Trump%20PAC%20last%20year.%20After%20Trump's%20election%20in%20November%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F12%2F06%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-elon-musk-silicon-valley.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20president-elect%20on%20intelligence%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaguire%20also%20began%20talking%20more%20publicly%20about%20his%20Judaism%20%E2%80%94%20he%20added%20the%20last%20name%20Cohn%20after%20getting%20married%20in%202018%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20support%20for%20Zionism.%20(One%20colleague%20said%20that%20he%20had%20no%20idea%20Maguire%20was%20Jewish%20until%20he%20arrived%20at%20his%20wedding%20in%20Israel.)%20He%20became%20a%20leading%20tech%20voice%20agitating%20on%20behalf%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-very-good-at-key-element-of-winning-air-war-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20war%20aims%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20October%207%2C%20Sequoia%20opened%20an%20office%20in%20Israel%2C%20and%20Maguire%20traveled%20there%20regularly%2C%20leading%20investments%20in%20cybersecurity%20and%20military%20firms.%20Maguire%20helped%20lead%20a%20%2410%20million%20seed%20round%20in%20Kela%2C%20a%20defense%20tech%20company%20founded%20by%20what%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20called%20%26quot%3Btechnowarriors%26quot%3B%20from%20elite%20Israeli%20military%20units.%20Kela%20produces%20sensors%20and%20AI%20systems%20that%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%94%20its%20website%20touts%20that%20its%20technology%20is%20%26quot%3Bbattle%20tested%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reflects%20the%20increased%20interest%20from%20American%20VCs%20in%20Israeli%20startups%20closely%20tied%20to%20the%20country's%20ongoing%20war%20with%20Hamas%20and%20its%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20at%20Sequoia%20had%20independently%20formed%20a%20thesis%20around%20Israeli%20defense%20tech%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20and%20two%20colleagues%20wrote%20in%20an%20article%20on%20Sequoia's%20website.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20the%20ambition%20is%20to%20convert%20Israel%20into%20a%20defense%20tech%20hub%20for%20Western%20militaries%20%E2%80%94%20a%20source%20of%20strategic%20advantage%20for%20NATO%20and%20the%20US%20as%20they%20seek%20to%20deter%20their%20adversaries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20thesis%20sits%20uncomfortably%20for%20some%20who%20don't%20share%20Maguire's%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20two%20years%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20painful%20and%20just%20demoralizing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hosam%20Arab%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20founder%20of%20fintech%20startup%20Tabby%2C%20who%20signed%20the%20open%20letter%20to%20Sequoia%20management.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20tech%20industry%20has%20essentially%20proscribed%20pro-Palestinian%20activism%20while%20broadly%20supporting%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BYou%20see%20what's%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20you%20just%20don't%20get%20the%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20predicament%20for%20startup%20founders%20working%20in%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you're%20worried%20about%20speaking%20out.%26quot%3B%20(Tabby%2C%20which%20is%20based%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20has%20received%20investment%20capital%20from%20Sequoia%20India%2C%20which%20has%20since%20become%20independent%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsequoia-capital-generative-artificial-intelligence-boom-venture-capital-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESequoia%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Muslim%20and%20South%20Asian%20tech%20executives%20I%20talked%20to%20worried%20that%20they%20could%20be%20fired%20for%20posting%20pro-Palestinian%20messages%20on%20social%20media.%20They%20described%20a%20culture%20of%20fear%20in%20which%20they%20believe%20only%20the%20most%20successful%20%E2%80%94%20founders%20%E2%80%94%20could%20speak%20out%20without%20experiencing%20major%20blowback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20was%20Amjad%20Masad%2C%20CEO%20of%20billion-dollar%20AI%20coding%20startup%20Replit%2C%20who%20recently%20talked%20about%20Gaza%20during%20an%20appearance%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-key-points-elon-musk-interview-joe-rogan-doge-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJoe%20Rogan's%20show%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20X%2C%20Maguire%20wrote%20that%20Masad%2C%20whose%20father%20is%20Palestinian%2C%20had%20lied%20to%20Rogan's%20vast%20audience%20about%20a%20massacre%20of%20Palestinians%20at%20an%20aid%20site.%20Masad%20shot%20back%20that%20Maguire's%20comment%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20slanderous%20lie%2C%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20a%20misleading%20screenshot.%20Khosla%20Ventures%20partner%20Keith%20Rabois%2C%20who%20has%20compared%20Masad%20to%20a%20Nazi%2C%20later%20joined%20the%20digital%20melee%2C%20calling%20Masad%20a%20Hamas%20supporter.%20Khosla%20Ventures%20is%20an%20investor%20in%20Masad's%20company.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20I'm%20Hamas%20supporter%20why%20don't%20you%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20Or%20are%20you%20a%20coward%3F%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Masad.%20(Masad%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20its%20investments%2C%20Sequoia%20has%20participated%20in%20two%20funding%20rounds%20for%20nsave%2C%20which%20provides%20digital%20banking%20services%20to%20people%20from%20%26quot%3Bdistressed%20economies%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20The%20company%20was%20started%20by%20two%20Rhodes%20scholars%20from%20Syria%20and%20Gaza.%20Nsave's%20Palestinian%20cofounder%20Abdullah%20AbuHashem%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sequoia%20can%20likely%20weather%20the%20media%20storm%2C%20Muslim%20tech%20workers%2C%20including%20at%20Sequoia%20portfolio%20companies%2C%20are%20beginning%20to%20organize%20alongside%20like-minded%20allies.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20producing%20groups%20that%20advocate%20for%20Palestine%20in%20some%20part%20of%20the%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Biggar%2C%20likening%20Tech%20for%20Palestine%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fy-combinator-yc-demo-day-spring-ai-agent-startups-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EY%20Combinator%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20activist%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaguire's%20volubility%20has%20struck%20some%20observers%20as%20out%20of%20character%20with%20a%20VC%20class%20that%20once%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20quantitative%2C%20measured%2C%20profit-seeking%20%E2%80%94%20and%20politically%20agnostic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20genuinely%20thought%20he%20was%20a%20shit%20poster%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20executive%20at%20a%20Sequoia%20portfolio%20company%2C%20who%20learned%20about%20Maguire%20through%20his%20X%20posts.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20idea%20he%20was%20an%20investor%20until%20very%20recently.%20I%20could%20not%20believe%20it.%20I%20thought%20this%20had%20to%20be%20a%20podcaster%20of%20some%20sort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%2C%20who%20is%20an%20Indian%20Hindu%2C%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20certain%20broad%20acceptance%20that%20firms%20like%20Sequoia%20would%20do%20business%20in%20Israel.%20The%20issue%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20is%20that%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Sequoia%20%26quot%3Bvisibly%20entering%20the%20end-of-days%20culture%20wars%20as%20a%20pundit%26quot%3B%20indicates%20that%20Sequoia%20might%20not%20just%20be%20following%20the%20money.%20%26quot%3BHe%20actually%20is%20saying%20out%20loud%20what%20is%20coalescing%20into%20a%20real%20capital%20structure.%26quot%3B%20The%20sectors%20Maguire%20invested%20in%20%E2%80%94%20cyber%2C%20space%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%