%20can%20access%20as%20they%20get%20older.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20Panama%20school%20offers%20international%20university%20advising%20once%20kids%20hit%20high%20school%2C%20in%20which%20they%20invite%20universities%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20to%20speak%20with%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20she%20said%2C%20most%20US%20schools%20teach%20a%20standard%20life%20formula%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20go%20to%20high%20school%2C%20you%20go%20to%20college%2C%20and%20you%20stay%20here%20and%20you%20get%20a%20job%2C%20and%20this%20is%20where%20you%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Oberlin%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhereas%20here%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20they%20truly%20are%20expanding%20their%20horizons%2C%20where%20they%20could%20go%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20to%20college%2C%20and%20they%20could%20do%20anything.%20So%20I%20definitely%20do%20think%20it's%20more%20globally%20aware%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d0cc376-0bc6-474c-a701-ec8265557872%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaryland%20to%20New%20Zealand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elissa%20Johnsen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6878f9daf748d8c055f5c815%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElissa%20Johnsen%20said%20her%20kids%20are%20better%20off%20after%20moving%20to%20New%20Zealand%20from%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Elissa%20Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20went%20into%20Elissa%20Johnsen's%20decision%20to%20move%20from%20Maryland%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%202022.%20Johnsen%20was%20working%20as%20a%20nurse%20during%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20took%20a%20severe%20mental%20toll.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20there%20was%20a%20school%20shooting%20at%20the%20high%20school%20right%20next%20to%20her%20daughter's%20elementary%20school%20in%202020%2C%20and%20Johnsen%20said%20the%20frequent%20lockdown%20drills%20were%20weig