%22%3Einfused%20himself%20with%20blood%20from%20his%20son%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20slow%20down%20his%20aging.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-bryan-johnson-stops-blood-infusions-young-people-teen-son-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estopped%20the%20transfusions%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20six%20months%2C%20saying%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bno%20benefits%20detected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20company%20sells%20a%20variety%20of%20wellness%20products.%20These%20include%20a%20%2455%20%26quot%3Blongevity%20mix%26quot%3B%20drink%20and%20a%20%2442%20mushroom%20coffee%20alternative%20they%20call%20%26quot%3BSuper%20Shrooms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Johnson%20announced%20on%20X%20that%20he%20was%20starting%20his%20own%20religion%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Die.%26quot%3B%20The%20name%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20slogan%20Johnson%20used%20to%20brand%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-bryan-johnson-home-netflix-doc-dont-die-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%20documentary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbryan-johnson-anti-aging-blueprint-olive-oil-longevity-braintree-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproducts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-bryan-johnson-dont-die-summit-singapore-longevity-health-biohacking-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eevents%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYears%20ago%2C%20I%20did%20a%20thought%20experiment%20imagining%20myself%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20people%20from%20the%2025th%20century.%20It%20seemed%20obvious%20that%20they'd%20say%20Don't%20Die%20is%20how%20humanity%20saved%20itself%20and%20merged%20with%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20however%2C%20says%20he's%20beginning%20to%20see%20how%20running%20a%20longevity-focused%20business%20may%20not%20mesh%20with%20preachin